The paper deals with optimization of antenna selection in a MIMO relay channel, which falls under the information theory (cs.IT) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses limited feedback, which is relevant to the systems and control (cs.SY) sub-category. The comparison of different beamforming techniques involves signal processing (cs.MM) and communication (cs.COM) sub-categories.
